title: SF SHIPYARD | 2BD/2BA | TWO LEVEL TOWNHOME | Rob Orlando SFRES
posting_body: 2Bedroom, 2Bath Townhome at SF Shipyard.
Features of this Wonderful Townhome Include:
The Main Level has a Living Room/Dining Area and Kitchen.
The Living Area is good size with an open floor plan.
The Kitchen overlooks the Living area and is fully equipped with stainless steel appliances.
There is a dining area off of the kitchen.
Also off of the Kitchen is a private balcony.
Upstairs has 2 Bedrooms both with en-suite Bathrooms.
One of the Bedrooms has a large walk-in closet and private balcony.
A Private Garage is on the ground floor level with Washer & Dryer.
This Luxuriously appointed residence, for the style-conscious urban dweller, has Graceful lines and architectural details bespeaking well-crafted elegance.
Open floor plan fusing classic and modern designs.
Sustainable Plyboo flooring throughout kitchen and living areas.

Modern, European-style Barbosa cabinetry with clean lines and generous storage Stainless steel Bosch appliances including gas range, hood, refrigerator, and dishwasher Gorgeous elongated ceramic tile backsplash with glass tile accent Quartz slab countertops with under mount sink in bathrooms.
Lustrous porcelain floors with glass accent tile.
